# Rust / Cargo build artifacts
/target
**/target
**/*.rs.bk

# Cargo lockfile is committed (required for reproducible builds in a workspace)
# Cargo.lock

# Persistent runtime data (sessions, checkpoints, memory snapshots)
# TaskExecutor writes JSON files here — never commit user/runtime state
data/
storage/
sessions/

# Environment / secrets (future-proof, even though we are zero-cloud)
.env
.env.local

# Logs
*.log
logs/

# Editor / IDE files
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# OS generated files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Temporary files
*.tmp
*.temp

# Test coverage / profiling (if we add later)
*.profraw
*.profdata

# AI Assistants
*_INSTRUCT.txt
AGENTS.md
PLAN.md
MEMORY.md

# Developer Only Documentation
# TESTING_PLAN.md